Definition: small slender woolly annual with very narrow opposite leaves and branches bearing solitary golden-yellow flower heads
Example: southwestern Oregon to Baja California and Arizona; often cultivated
Synonyms: Lasthenia_chrysostoma, wildflower, genus_Lasthenia, m, small, slender, woolly, annual, with, very, narrow, opposite, leaves, and, branches, bearing, solitary, golden-yellow, flower, heads, southwestern, Oregon, to, Baja, California, Arizona, often, cultivated
Category: noun.plant
